 Leap Year Checker (Java)
This project contains a simple Java program that checks whether a given year is a leap year according to the standard rules.

## ðŸ“– Description
- Prompts the user to enter a year (integer)
- Determines if the year is a leap year using multiple conditions:
  - A year is a leap year if it is divisible by 4 **and not** divisible by 100, **or** it is divisible by 400
- Prints whether the year is a leap year or not
- Handles typical examples:
  - 2000 â†’ leap year
  - 1900 â†’ not a leap year
  - 2004 â†’ leap year
